CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 16, 1941, pg. 10, reads: "The Saturday Supper club party at Loendi Saturday evening closed the eventful Frog Week. Right photo shows the members of the club, left to right: Mrs. Susie McNeal, Mrs. Ada Brown, Mrs. Florence Lewis, Mrs. Agatha Sims, Mrs. Winifred Houston, Mrs. Jereline Henry, Mrs. Agnes Stevenson, Mrs. Marie Hamilton and Mrs. Harriett [Harriet] Lewis.... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Susie McNeal, Ada Brown, Florence Lewis, Agatha Sims, Winifred Houston, Jereline Henry, Agnes Stevenson, Marie Hamilton, and Harriet Lewis on right, posed in Loendi Club, another version
